Glitter Paper Table Runner

Make your tablescape ooze festive shine and opulent style statement with our sparkling range of Glitter Table Runners. Featuring chic geometric honeycomb pattern on glimmering glittered surface, this deluxe runner will dress your dining and party tables to the nines.

Elegant and Stylish

Easy to use and elegant in impact. No need to iron or launder, this wrinkle resistant and water repellent runner makes setting an opulent tablescape a breeze. Stylishly spread atop your bare or clothed tables to give an elegant elite look without breaking the banks.

Multi-purpose and Versatile

Majestic in effect and multipurpose in application, this sturdy runner can be used to glam up your coffee table, dining table, kitchen table, party tables, banquet tables, and wedding tables. For a truly exotic look and effect, pair these shimmering beauties with matching glitter accented table linens, chair covers and belts, napkins, centerpieces, and candles.
